<h1 class='c-primaryTitle s-marginTop1_5 blog-posts-show-header__title'>
Republic acquires Fig
</h1>
<p class='c-subtitle s-marginTop1_5 blog-posts-show-header__subtitle'>
Fig is a groundbreaking publishing platform that lets video game fans invest in returns from games they back through Fig and be rewarded for their success.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='blog-posts-show-header__cover-column' style='background-image: url(https://uploads.republic.com/p/blog/posts/cover_photos/large_retina/000/000/198/198-1587044297-660a8c9dd03c7f225e6ca24e7c54cdfc23f9d66e.jpg)'></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class='s-container s-gridMaxXs24'>
<div class='s-grid s-marginBottom4' data-sticky-container>
<div class='s-grid-colMd4 s-marginPullTop1 u-hiddenSmDown'>
